  <summary date="2022-11-23T20:46:30Z" status="Introduced in House">Make Energy Affordable Act

This bill requires the President to report on the rising energy prices. In addition, the President must provide updates on residential energy price trends, impacts of energy prices on low-income households, and actions by federal agencies to mitigate energy price increases.</summary>
